<h1>愿</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">yuàn</span><span class=alesi>(yuan4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 愿 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 愿</h2><div class=abo>
